frontmatter.title: Three JS Dance Floor
frontmatter.image_alt: Image of dance floor with character dancing
frontmatter.excerpt:
First project using Three JS, a Javascript library for putting 3D content on the web. Well poking around the examples I saw one with a mesh dancing and got the idea to incorporate the first 3D mesh I made in Blender.
The few hours I worked on this makes me far from a pro, so this is just a some links I found helpful.
